## 2. Cover handoff creation in `handleCallback`

This requires mocking the `WebClient` chain. Add mocks:

```java
@Mock private WebClient.RequestBodyUriSpec requestBodyUriSpec;
@Mock private WebClient.RequestBodySpec requestBodySpec;
@Mock private WebClient.RequestHeadersSpec<?> requestHeadersSpec;
@Mock private WebClient.ResponseSpec responseSpec;
```

Then test:

```java
@Test
void shouldCreateSessionAndLoginHandoffDuringCallback() {
    AuthTransaction tx = new AuthTransaction();
    tx.setAppId("B2BOOST_BE");
    tx.setRedirectUri("http://arthur/callback");
    tx.setCodeVerifier("VERIFIER123");

    AppConfigResponse appConfig = validAppConfig();

    OidcMetadata metadata = new OidcMetadata();
    metadata.setTokenEndpoint("http://keycloak.kubernetes.localhost/token");

    JwtUserClaims claims = new JwtUserClaims();
    claims.setPreferredUsername("testuser");

    UserResponse user = new UserResponse();
    user.setUserId("testuser");
    user.setUsername("testuser");
    user.setRoles(List.of("SELLER"));

    Map<String, Object> tokenResponse = new HashMap<>();
    tokenResponse.put("access_token", "ACCESS_TOKEN");
    tokenResponse.put("id_token", "ID_TOKEN");
    tokenResponse.put("refresh_token", "REFRESH_TOKEN");

    when(redisAuthTransactionService.findByState("STATE123")).thenReturn(tx);
    when(lancelotClient.getApp("B2BOOST_BE")).thenReturn(appConfig);
    when(oidcDiscoveryClient.loadMetadata("http://issuer")).thenReturn(metadata);

    when(webClient.post()).thenReturn(requestBodyUriSpec);
    when(requestBodyUriSpec.uri(anyString())).thenReturn(requestBodySpec);
    when(requestBodySpec.contentType(any())).thenReturn(requestBodySpec);
    when(requestBodySpec.body(any())).thenReturn((WebClient.RequestHeadersSpec) requestHeadersSpec);
    when(requestHeadersSpec.retrieve()).thenReturn(responseSpec);
    when(responseSpec.onStatus(any(), any())).thenReturn(responseSpec);
    when(responseSpec.bodyToMono(any(ParameterizedTypeReference.class)))
            .thenReturn(Mono.just(tokenResponse));

    when(jwtService.extractClaims("ID_TOKEN")).thenReturn(claims);
    when(lancelotClient.getUserById("testuser")).thenReturn(user);

    AuthResult result = authService.handleCallback("CODE123", "STATE123");

    assertNotNull(result.getSessionId());
    assertEquals("http://frontend/home", result.getPostLoginRedirectUrl());
    assertNotNull(result.getHandoffCode());

    verify(redisSessionService).save(any(UserSession.class));
    verify(redisLoginHandoffService).save(any(LoginHandoff.class));
    verify(redisAuthTransactionService).delete("STATE123");
}
```

